Compile a folder of templates to a similar output folder

Usage:
  kojo dir INDIR [--save DIR --import DIR --args FILE] [ARGS...]
  kojo dir (-h|--help)

Options:
  -s --save DIR
    Save output to directory instead of printing

  -i --import DIR
    Specify base directory for @import directives

  -a --args FILE
    Load arguments from YAML file

  -h --help
    Show this help

Parameters:
  ARGS
    Optional key=value pairs

Examples:
  kojo dir indir
  kojo dir in --save out env=production
  kojo dir in --save out --import snippets env=production
  kojo dir in -s out -i snippets -a args.yml
